\c 9
\s UEzra uyakuvuma ukona kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli
\p
\v 1 Ngosuku lwamatshumi amabili lane lwaleyonyanga\x + 8.2.\x* abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebebuthana ngokuzila ukudla\x + 1 Sam. 7.6.\x*, langamasaka\x + 1 Kho. 20.31.\x*, lenhlabathi phezu kwabo\x + Josh. 7.6.\x*.
\v 2 Inzalo yakoIsrayeli yasizehlukanisa labo bonke abezizweni; basebesima bavuma izono zabo lobubi baboyise\x + 13.3,30. Ezra 10.11.\x*.
\v 3 Basebesukuma endaweni yabo yokuma\x + 8.7.\x*, bafunda egwalweni lomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wabo ingxenye yesine yosuku; njalo ngengxenye yesine bavuma futhi bakhonza iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wabo\x + 8.7,8,18. 13.1.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Lezikhwelweni zamaLevi kwakumi oJeshuwa\x + 8.7.\x*, loBani\x + 8.7.\x*, uKadimiyeli\x + Ezra 2.40.\x*, uShebaniya\x + 10.10,12. 12.3,14.\x*, uBuni\x + 10.15.\x*, uSherebiya\x + Ezra 8.18.\x*, uBani\x + 8.7.\x*, uKenani; bamemeza ngelizwi elikhulu eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wabo.
\v 5 AmaLevi, oJeshuwa\x + 8.7.\x*, loKadimiyeli\x + Ezra 2.40.\x*, uBani\x + 8.7.\x*, uHashabineya\x + 3.10. 10.25.\x*, uSherebiya\x + Ezra 8.18.\x*, uHodiya\x + 8.7.\x*, uShebaniya\x + 10.10,12. 12.3,14.\x*, uPethahiya\x + Ezra 10.23.\x* basebesithi: Sukumani libusise iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu kusukela ephakadeni kuze kube nininini; kalibusiswe ibizo lakho elilodumo eliphakanyiswe phezu kwaso sonke isibusiso lendumiso\x + 1 Lan. 29.13.\x*.
\v 6 Nguwe oyiN\nd kosi\nd* wena wedwa\x + 2 Kho. 19.15.\x*, wena wenza amazulu\x + Gen. 1.1. Isam. 14.7.\x*, izulu lamazulu\x + Dute. 10.14.\x* lalo lonke ibutho lawo, umhlaba lakho konke okukuwo, izinlwandle lakho konke okukuzo\x + Gen. 2.1.\x*, wena uyagcina konke kuphila; lebutho lamazulu liyakukhonza\x + Hlab. 36.6.\x*.
\v 7 Wena uyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu, owakhetha uAbrama wamkhupha eUri yamaKhaladiya\x + Gen. 11.31. 12.1.\x*, wenza ibizo lakhe laba nguAbrahama\x + Gen. 17.5.\x*;
\v 8 wafica inhliziyo yakhe ithembekile phambi kwakho\x + Gen. 15.6.\x*, wenza laye isivumelwano\x + Gen. 12.7. 15.18. 17.7-9.\x* sokunika ilizwe lamaKhanani, amaHethi, amaAmori, lamaPerizi, lamaJebusi, lamaGirigashi, ukulinika inzalo yakhe\x + Eks. 13.5.\x*; uwamisile amazwi akho, ngoba ulungile\x + Josh. 23.14.\x*.
\v 9 Wabona ukuhlupheka kwabobaba eGibhithe\x + Eks. 3.7.\x*, wezwa ukukhala kwabo ngasoLwandle oluBomvu\x + Eks. 14.10.\x*,
\v 10 wenza izibonakaliso lezimangaliso kuFaro lakuzo zonke inceku zakhe lakubo bonke abantu belizwe lakhe\x + Eks. 7,8,9,10,12,14.\x*, ngoba wazi ukuthi baziphatha ngokuzigqaja kubo\x + 9.16,29. Eks. 18.11.\x*; njalo wazenzela ibizo njengalamuhla\x + Isa. 63.12,14. Jer. 32.20. Dan. 9.15. Eks. 9.16. 1 Lan. 17.21.\x*.
\v 11 Wehlukanisa ulwandle phambi kwabo ukuze bachaphe phakathi kolwandle emhlabathini owomileyo\x + Eks. 14.21,22,27,28.\x*; wasuphosela ababaxotshayo ezinzikini njengelitshe emanzini alamandla\x + Eks. 15.5. Eks. 15.10.\x*.
\v 12 Wasubakhokhela ngensika yeyezi emini langensika yomlilo ebusuku ukubakhanyisela indlela abazahamba ngayo\x + 9.19. Eks. 13.21,22. Nani 14.14. 1 Kor. 10.1.\x*.
\v 13 Wehlela phezu kwentaba yeSinayi, wakhuluma labo usemazulwini\x + Eks. 19.20. 20.1.\x*, wabanika izahlulelo eziqondileyo, lemilayo eqotho, izimiso lemilayezelo elungileyo\x + Hlab. 19.8,9. Roma 7.12.\x*,
\v 14 wabazisa isabatha lakho elingcwele, wabalaya imilayo, lezimiso, lomthetho, ngesandla sikaMozisi inceku yakho\x + Eks. 16.23. Eks. 20.8-11. Hez. 20.12,20.\x*.
\v 15 Wabanika isinkwa esivela emazulwini ekulambeni kwabo\x + Eks. 16.14,15. Joha. 6.31.\x*, lamanzi edwaleni wabakhuphela wona ekomeni kwabo\x + Eks. 17.6. Nani 20.9.\x*; wabatshela ukuthi bazangena badle ilifa lelizwe owaphakamisa isandla sakho ukubanika lona\x + Dute. 1.8.\x*.
\v 16 Kodwa bona labobaba baziphatha ngokuzigqaja\x + 9.10,29. Hlab. 106.6.\x*, benza lukhuni intamo yabo, kabayilalelanga imilayo yakho\x + 9.17,29. 2 Lan. 30.8.\x*.
\v 17 Yebo, bala ukulalela, kabakhumbulanga izimangaliso zakho owazenza kubo\x + Hlab. 78.11,42,43.\x*; kodwa bazenza lukhuni intamo yabo\x + 9.17,29. 2 Lan. 30.8.\x*, lekuvukeleni kwabo bamisa induna ukuze babuyele ebugqilini babo\x + Nani 14.4.\x*. Kodwa wena unguNkulunkulu wezintethelelo, olomusa, lesihawu\x + 9.31. Eks. 34.6. Jow. 2.13.\x*, ophuza ukuthukuthela\x + 9.31. Eks. 34.6. Jow. 2.13.\x*, lowande ngothando, kawubatshiyanga\x + Nani 14.18. Eks. 22.27.\x*.
\v 18 Lalapho sebezenzele ithole elibunjwe ngokuncibilikisa bathi: Lo nguNkulunkulu wakho, owakwenyusa eGibhithe\x + Eks. 32.4.\x*, benza ukuhlambaza okukhulu\x + 9.26. 2 Kho. 19.3.\x*,
\v 19 kodwa wena ngezihawu zakho ezinengi kawubatshiyanga enkangala\x + 9.27,31. Hlab. 106.45.\x*; insika yeyezi kayisukanga kubo emini, ukubakhokhela endleleni, lensika yomlilo ebusuku, ukubakhanyisela lendlela abazahamba ngayo\x + 9.12.\x*.
\v 20 Wabanika umoya wakho omuhle ukubafundisa\x + Isa. 63.11. Nani 11.17.\x*, lemana yakho kawuyigodlanga emlonyeni wabo\x + 9.15. Josh. 5.12.\x*, wabanika amanzi ekomeni kwabo\x + 9.15. Josh. 5.12.\x*.
\v 21 Yebo, iminyaka engamatshumi amane wabondla enkangala, kabaswelanga \add lutho\x + Dute. 2.7.\x*\add*; izigqoko zabo kaziguganga, lenyawo zabo kazivuvukanga\x + Dute. 8.4. 29.5.\x*.
\v 22 Wasebanika imibuso lezizwe, wababela kwaze kwaba semagumbini\x + Nani 24.17. Jer. 48.45.\x*; njalo badla ilifa lelizwe likaSihoni\x + Nani 21.21.\x* lelizwe lenkosi yeHeshiboni\x + Nani 32.37.\x* lelizwe likaOgi inkosi yeBashani\x + Nani 21.33-35.\x*.
\v 23 Wandisa abantwana babo njengenkanyezi zamazulu, wabangenisa elizweni owawutshele oyise ukuthi bazangena badle ilifa lalo\x + Gen. 15.5.\x*.
\v 24 Sebengenile abantwana babo badla ilifa lelizwe\x + Josh. 1.2.\x*; wehlisela phansi phambi kwabo abahlali belizwe, amaKhanani, wabanikela esandleni sabo, lamakhosi abo, labantu belizwe, ukuze benze ngabo ngokwentando yabo\x + Hlab. 44.2,3.\x*.
\v 25 Basebethumba imizi ebiyelweyo, lelizwe elivundileyo\x + 9.35. Nani 13.27. Dute. 8.7,8. Hez. 20.6.\x*, badla ilifa lezindlu ezigcwele konke okuhle, imithombo egejiweyo, izivini, lezivande zemihlwathi, lezihlahla zezithelo ngobunengi\x + Dute. 6.11.\x*. Badla-ke basutha, bazimuka\x + Dute. 32.15.\x*, bazithokozisa ngokuhle kwakho okukhulu\x + 9.35. 2 Lan. 6.41. Hos. 3.5.\x*.
\v 26 Kube kanti kabalalelanga, bakuvukela wena\x + Hlu. 2.11,12. Hez. 20.21.\x*, bawuphosela umlayo wakho emva komhlana wabo\x + 1 Kho. 14.9.\x*, babulala abaprofethi bakho abafakaza bemelene labo ukubaphendulela kuwe\x + 1 Kho. 18.4. 19.10. 2 Lan. 24.20,21. Mat. 23.37. Seb. 7.52.\x*, benza ukuhlambaza okukhulu\x + 9.18.\x*.
\v 27 Ngakho wabanikela esandleni sezitha zabo ezabahluphayo\x + Hlu. 2.14. 3.8,9. Hlab. 106.41,42,44.\x*; kwathi ngesikhathi sokuhlupheka kwabo bakhala kuwe, wena-ke wezwa usemazulwini; langokwezisa zakho ezinengi\x + 9.19,31.\x* wabanika abasindisi ababasindisa esandleni sezitha zabo\x + Hlu. 3.9.\x*.
\v 28 Kodwa sebephumulile benza okubi futhi phambi kwakho; ngakho wabatshiya esandleni sezitha zabo zaze zababusa; sebebuyile bakhala kuwe, wena wezwa usemazulwini\x + Hlu. 3.11,12,30. 4.1. 5.31. 6.1.\x*; wabakhulula ngokwezisa zakho izikhathi ezinengi\x + Hlab. 106.43.\x*.
\v 29 Wafakaza umelene labo ukuze ubenze babuyele emlayweni wakho; kube kanti bona baziphatha ngokuzigqaja, kabayilalelanga imilayo yakho\x + 9.10,16.\x*, kodwa bemelene lezahlulelo zakho bona bemelene lazo (okuthi umuntu ezenza uzaphila ngazo\x + Levi 18.5.\x*), banika ihlombe lobuqholo, benza lukhuni intamo yabo, kabaze balalela\x + 9.16,17.\x*.
\v 30 Wababekezelela\f + \fk wababekezelela: \fl Heb. \fq wadonsa ngabo.\f* iminyaka eminengi, wafakaza umelene labo ngomoya wakho\x + 9.26,29,34. 2 Kho. 17.13.\x* ngesandla sabaprofethi bakho, kodwa kababekanga indlebe\x + 2 Lan. 36.15. 1 Pet. 1.11. 2 Pet. 1.21.\x*. Ngakho wabanikela esandleni sabantu bezizwe\x + Ezra 9.7.\x*.
\v 31 Kanti ngezisa zakho ezinengi\x + 9.19,27.\x* kawubaqedanga, kawubatshiyanga\x + Jer. 4.27.\x*; ngoba unguNkulunkulu olomusa\x + 9.17.\x* lesihawu\x + Dute. 4.31.\x*.
\v 32 Ngakho khathesi, Nkulunkulu wethu, uNkulunkulu omkhulu, olamandla lowesabekayo\x + Dute. 7.21.\x*, ogcina isivumelwano lomusa\x + Dute. 7.9. Eks. 34.6,7.\x*, kakungabi kuncinyane phambi kwakho ukuhlupheka konke, okusificileyo, amakhosi ethu, iziphathamandla zethu, labapristi bethu, labaprofethi bethu, labobaba, labo bonke abantu bakho, kusukela ensukwini zamakhosi eAsiriya kuze kube lamuhla\x + 2 Kho. 17.3.\x*.
\v 33 Kodwa ubulungile mayelana lakho konke okusehleleyo, ngoba wenzile ngokuqonda\x + Ezra 9.15.\x*, kodwa thina senze ngobubi\x + Hlab. 106.6. Dan. 9.5.\x*.
\v 34 Lamakhosi ethu, iziphathamandla zethu, abapristi bethu, labobaba bethu kabawenzanga umlayo wakho, kabalalelanga imithetho yakho lezifakazelo zakho owazifakaza umelene labo.
\v 35 Ngoba bona kabakukhonzanga embusweni wabo\x + Dute. 28.47.\x* lekulungeni kwakho okunengi owabanika khona\x + 9.25.\x* lemazweni abanzi lavundileyo owawabeka phambi kwabo; njalo kabaphendukanga ezenzweni zabo ezimbi\x + 9.25.\x*.
\v 36 Khangela, siyizigqili lamuhla, yebo, ilizwe owalinika obaba ukuthi badle isithelo salo lokuhle kwalo, khangela, siyizigqili kulo\x + Ezra 9.9.\x*.
\v 37 Njalo isivuno salo lisandisela amakhosi owabeke phezu kwethu ngenxa yezono zethu; njalo abusa phezu kwemizimba yethu laphezu kwezifuyo zethu ngokwentando yawo; sesisesizini olukhulu\x + Dute. 28.33,48,51.\x*.
\v 38 Langenxa yakho konke lokhu senza \add isivumelwano\add* esiqinileyo, sisibhala; iziphathamandla zethu, amaLevi ethu, abapristi bethu, basebefaka uphawu phezu kwaso\x + 10.29. 2 Kho. 23.3. 2 Lan. 29.10.34.31. Ezra 10.3.\x*.
